{"tid":1129031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【4.28上街】黎智英李柱銘參與遊行 陳日君：勿小覷每個人微小力量","createTime":"2019-04-28T08:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T08:22:01.000Z","uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"731b93bb548b65e4053e861980d336b68c87305c","tid":1129031,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190428/59539660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190428%2F59539660&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=80f32584\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190428%2F59539660&h=82cac967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190428/59539660</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民陣今日發起反「送中」惡法遊行，香港天主教正義和平委員會在遊行前舉行祈禱會，逾70人出席，包括天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機。陳日君婉拒接受訪問，向教友致辭時寄語教友不要小覷每一個人的力量微小。壹傳媒創辦人黎智英及資深大律師、民主黨創黨主席李柱銘亦有參與遊行。"}]}